author: James Rogers
title: Coronavirus social distancing buying valuable time for scientists in hunt for cure: Biochemist
description: Effective social distancing is buying valuable time for the medical community in its hunt for a coronavirus cure, according to Isaiah “Shy” Arkin, professor of Structural Biochemistry at the Hebrew University of Jerusalem.
